description: A playful spin on how winter jokes bring warmth.
title: Warm Laughs
n_1: Eddy chuckles at the snowy scene outside.
n_2: May giggles as Eddy shares a joke.
c2_2: Because they have snow many layers?
n_3: They laugh, feeling cozy despite the chill.
n_4: Their laughter fills the warm room, overlooking the cold.
c1_4: These jokes make us warm inside!
c2_4: It's the joy of winter humor.
